casebody.data:
STATE EX REL. Glenn YOUNG
v.
STATE of Louisiana NO. 2017-KH-1958 Supreme Court of Louisiana. January 8, 2019 Denied. Relator has previously exhausted his right to state collateral review and fails to show that any exception permits his successive filing. See State ex rel. Young v. State, 14-2603 (La. 10/30/15), 178 So.3d 135 . JOHNSON, C.J., would grant.
